replies.body:
Thank you for confirming that for me. Since you're still having issues, this is likely a more complicated issue that we'll need to take a look at system logs in order to resolve. I recommend grabbing some logs by running our [Hextech Tool](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/224826367) then attach the file it outputs to a [support ticket.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new)

One of our tech specialists will be happy to assist you from here out. Let me know if you have any questions.
